query:
INSERT INTO app.projects (
                            name,
                            visibility,
                            country_code,
                            crs_srid,
                            owner,
                            added_by,
                            last_updated_by,
                            slug,
                            team_id
                            )
                    VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $5, $5, $6,
                            (SELECT team_id FROM app.users WHERE id = $5)
                )
                RETURNING id AS "id: ProjectId"
